sect2.para:
Some themes (Maw, Black E) have an
      actionclasses.cfg like: 
#include <definitions>
__E_CFG_VERSION 0
#include </usr/local/enlightenment/config/actionclasses.cfg>
#include </usr/share/enlightenment/config/actionclasses.cfg>
       The absolute path is obviously no longer valid. The
      most sensible fix for these themes is to remove the themes
      actionclasses.cfg. e16
      will then fall back to the default one.
